{"tid":1526010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［831恐襲］要求美國制裁全港3萬警蓄","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:29:44.000Z","uid":270768,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5963ce779536eb9fb04981d4226b65470aba50de","tid":1526010,"uid":270768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"香港警蓄行為無法無天，泯滅人性，等同恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n可否<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請求美帝</span></span></span>就「香港民主及人權法案」加入制裁港警條例，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港3萬港警及其家人將默認受到制裁</span></span>，再由美國主導在港設立可靠獨立調查委員會，清白港警要主動提供資料，証明自己從無參與任何鎮壓行動方可減輕制裁，主動提供違規警蓄資料及細節者甚至可獲制裁括免<br />\n<br />\n想法可能天真或唔周詳，但試問世上除咗美帝同支共，仲有咩人可以阻止呢班蛆蟲繼續作惡？"},{"pid":"af5ff4f2f3559a36fed4abcdb1af888840f50078","tid":1526010,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=2dc2535e\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05d359510332880ad52ff62809e04b5aad50807b","tid":1526010,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>凍結香港警察</strong>所有戶口<br />\n<strong>驅逐</strong>所有香港警察家人出境，永久唔可以入境美國"},{"pid":"c62e4520c105759f4fd47c09d1697639edc49421","tid":1526010,"uid":263186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"be35653f0128973bef75ecc71bf73df068f00c18","tid":1526010,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n英文好既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056ddcc780b01e9e03b30740e432f89fc21423fd","tid":1526010,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"11d81222575a63803241ea207e09eb71905cab89","tid":1526010,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"推到有英文好既手足"},{"pid":"5cda646155bb069b465655feaaa8eb9ebc4a2ee7","tid":1526010,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cae689c65312e267b16047f11ab66d650b8d5651","tid":1526010,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45ef4460cde54e62179fa87cac2736f92d0df5f","tid":1526010,"uid":219767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime